Primary neurite tracts (and accompanying metadata)

Source: R/physplitdata.R
primary_neurites.is2.Rd

primary_neurites.is2 is in the IS2 template brain space (Jefferis Lab).

primary_neurites.jfrc2 is in the JFRC2 template brain space (Janelia / Virtual Fly Brain).

primary_neurites.is2

primary_neurites.jfrc2

Format

An object of class neuronlist (inherits from list) of length 48.

Details

This is initally created by data-raw/pct.R which in turn depends on LHNTracing/R/MakeParentClusters.R.

See also

lhnsxfinal
